495
00:32:46.659 --> 00:32:48.859
Malamig ang pagkain, kumain.

496
00:32:51.466 --> 00:32:53.278
Ito ang 20,000 won na inutang ko sa iyo noong nakaraan.

497
00:32:53.278 --> 00:32:55.073
